channel.title: Making Client With One File Progress
channel.description:
Ok So I just started to make my server from scratch with one file. The reason is that, for my ideas to possibly be made in any other server, i would have to delete, just about 1/2 of everything, recode it, add it again, etc. So i decided to make my own. This Is Just a prgress log on.. well my prorgess. Dont Spam, and i can post this here. So Here it Is:
ZymusScape Server Progress:
Client: 4% Guilds: 23% Mini-Games: 0% Quests: 3% Skills: 12.5%
Im Always working. so i shoud be done in about 2 months, probably less.
